{"tid":84220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享靈異經歷","createTime":"2017-01-17T11:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T11:40:55.000Z","uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c80be8c2e9f7f965f1cc710ce4f893cba678c920","tid":84220,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"一齊講下自己/身邊人嘅靈異事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我細個發生過一件，聽呀媽講我細個同班親戚一齊去南丫島玩兩日一夜（好似係），夜晚訓覺我就喊得好犀利，啲親戚問我表姐咩事（佢訓我隔嚟），佢就話望到間房上面有啲影，見到係有一個男人行𡁵一條調轉嘅樓梯。即係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcyicgqASmmjoguJRkFJqV5AK3mZqemY5upiEmdYjmfxf?filename=0ZGS084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZGS084.jpg&h=9487f914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後番咗屋企嗰幾晚我都不斷發燒，睇醫生都唔退，我媽就偶爾同一個識得睇（嗰啲叫咩？）嘅人傾計，就話我身邊有個女人跟住，之後叫我媽喺屋企某個位燒衣紙，燒完就退左燒。<br />\n<br />\n之後會再講我媽同我表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe4da06d60767c3c94d209012b6fc5a78df8d60","tid":84220,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"我點個嗰啲叫咩呀"},{"pid":"61795d8e63f1f9334626f80f71ac29c4133c8920","tid":84220,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我點知嗰啲叫咩呀</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c557813bb0d081af4986003cdf5e3197fc03c5e9","tid":84220,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"姐係類似有陰陽眼嗰啲人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到身邊有污糟野嗰種<br />\nSorry for1999"},{"pid":"5306223d16761e1bc26fbe3afb3d66fbdcddd8a7","tid":84220,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"講下我媽<br />\n最深刻嘅一單係佢有次因爲工作關係去舊式工廠大廈，之後走嗰時佢想去個廁所啦，但個廁所要落地庫一層，本身佢都驚驚地但冇計啦急尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢快快手痾完尿出去洗手，洗手間啲鏡係反射望到門口出面部lift，之後咁啱見到部lift慢慢閂門，而裡面企左個短頭髮、著黑色唐裝嘅女人，個女人啲前陰仲要好長...長到落鼻，遮住晒對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想象嘅好似咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/193840_c8edccfc4cf9c22765ca076c42e91ae3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F193840_c8edccfc4cf9c22765ca076c42e91ae3.jpg&h=1b0b306e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2a47dbca0116644788f529b473c626978984a39","tid":84220,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身d 故事已經唔恐怖<br />\n<br />\n加埋d公仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}